## Relative Motion in 2 Dimensions
## Part 1
## 2-D Motion
## By F.Wolfs, WOLFS@NSRL31.NSRL.ROCHESTER.EDU
## No unauthorized commercial use.
## Imported Files:
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## Values needing defined:
